# ╺━━━╸
#   plumage/neon — the sign in the window
# tagline: one hot magenta tube, cyan glow, always open
#
# The only theme in the pack that runs a lit background segment,
# because a neon sign that isn't lit is just bent glass. The tube
# below fades cyan into magenta like it's bleeding light.

PROMPT='%K{201}%F{16} ⌁ %k%f %F{123}%n%F{240}·%F{201}${PLUMAGE_BOX}%f %F{240}⟨%F{87}%~%F{240}⟩%f
%F{51}╺%F{87}━%F{123}━%F{201}╸%f %(?.%F{201}.%F{203})❯%f '
